  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join the fight club!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/66c5fc1fdf73cddeb6a5ed46de6dcc4c.avif?t=1772360306\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Streets of Rageness is a reimagined '90s beat 'em up classic set in a crime-ridden city under the iron grip of a ruthless syndicate. Amid rampant looting, chaos, and destruction, fight through waves of thugs to become the most powerful fighter on the streets!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/9b6b64c4a82122fac9776583eae96e1a.webp?t=1772360306\" width=616 height=49 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/d8f2cd9ba2180794ac34fc8506fa560f.poster.avif?t=1772360306\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/d8f2cd9ba2180794ac34fc8506fa560f.webm?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/d8f2cd9ba2180794ac34fc8506fa560f.mp4?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Streets of Rageness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streets of Rageness takes the classic beat 'em up formula to a whole new level with immersive 3D environments and dynamic combat inspired by iconic fighting games like Street Fighter and Tekken. Step into the shoes of a diverse cast of street fighters, each with unique abilities and fighting styles, as you battle through a series of gritty, urban arenas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/85d9cc6336c2d6b009edf41b88672ccc.webp?t=1772360306\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/a970c8e2aa7ec3c980d443567714418e.poster.avif?t=1772360306\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/a970c8e2aa7ec3c980d443567714418e.webm?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/a970c8e2aa7ec3c980d443567714418e.mp4?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master powerful punch and kick combos, unleash devastating special moves, and engage in fast-paced brawls against waves of ruthless enemies. The game offers a visceral, adrenaline-pumping experience that captures old-school arcade action with a fresh twist. Explore detailed cityscapes, conquer challenging bosses, and prove yourself as the ultimate street warrior in this homage to the classic Streets of Rage series.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Streets of Rageness is a reimagined '90s beat 'em up classic set in a crime-ridden city under the iron grip of a ruthless syndicate. Amid rampant looting, chaos, and destruction, fight through waves of thugs to become the most powerful fighter on the streets!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/9b6b64c4a82122fac9776583eae96e1a.webp?t=1772360306\" width=616 height=49 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/d8f2cd9ba2180794ac34fc8506fa560f.poster.avif?t=1772360306\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/d8f2cd9ba2180794ac34fc8506fa560f.webm?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/d8f2cd9ba2180794ac34fc8506fa560f.mp4?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Streets of Rageness</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streets of Rageness takes the classic beat 'em up formula to a whole new level with immersive 3D environments and dynamic combat inspired by iconic fighting games like Street Fighter and Tekken. Step into the shoes of a diverse cast of street fighters, each with unique abilities and fighting styles, as you battle through a series of gritty, urban arenas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/85d9cc6336c2d6b009edf41b88672ccc.webp?t=1772360306\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/a970c8e2aa7ec3c980d443567714418e.poster.avif?t=1772360306\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/a970c8e2aa7ec3c980d443567714418e.webm?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210270/extras/a970c8e2aa7ec3c980d443567714418e.mp4?t=1772360306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master powerful punch and kick combos, unleash devastating special moves, and engage in fast-paced brawls against waves of ruthless enemies. The game offers a visceral, adrenaline-pumping experience that captures old-school arcade action with a fresh twist. Explore detailed cityscapes, conquer challenging bosses, and prove yourself as the ultimate street warrior in this homage to the classic Streets of Rage series.</p>",
